snippet.title: Dragon's Prophet Gamescom Trailer
snippet.description:
Dragons fly over Cologne for Gamescom, August 21-25, 2013. 

Dragon's Prophet's launch date is September 18, 2013. Sign up for beta at http://www.dragonsprophetthegame.com 
Dragon's Prophet is a free to play fantasy MMO that transports you to Auratia, a realm where dragons fill the sky.
